read_example_file.Rd

Read A eurobarometer Package Example File

This function is created to make panel data creation examples without relying on importing large SPSS files.

read_example_file(sample_file_name = "ZA7576_sample")

Arguments

sample_file_name

Any of ZA7576_sample, ZA6863_sample or ZA5913_sample.

Examples

read_example_file ( sample_file_name = 'ZA7576_sample' )
